 &lt;span class="k"&gt;fun&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;u&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;c&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="bp"&gt;↦&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="bp"&gt;∀&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;ε&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="bp"&gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="bp"&gt;∃&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;N&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="bp"&gt;∀&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;n&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="bp"&gt;≥&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;N&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;,&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="bp"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="n"&gt;u&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;n&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="bp"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;c&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="bp"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="bp"&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;ε&lt;/span&gt;

&lt;span class="kd"&gt;example&lt;/span&gt;
  &lt;span class="o"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;limite&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;u&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="bp"&gt;↔&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;limite&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="k"&gt;fun&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="bp"&gt;↦&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;u&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;i&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="bp"&gt;-&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="n"&gt;a&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class="o"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="mi"&gt;0&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="o"&gt;:=&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;span class="kd"&gt;by&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class="gr"&gt;sorry&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://jaalonso.github.io/calculemus/posts/2024/02/16-el_limite_de_u_es_a_syss_el_de_u-a_es_0/"&gt;Leer más…&lt;/a&gt; (quedan 4 minutos de lectura)&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><guid>https://jaalonso.github.io/calculemus/posts/2024/02/16-el_limite_de_u_es_a_syss_el_de_u-a_es_0/</guid><pubDate>Fri, 16 Feb 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate></item><item><title>Si el límite de la sucesión uₙ es a y c ∈ ℝ, entonces el límite de cuₙ es ca</title><link>https://jaalonso.github.io/calculemus/posts/2024/02/15-limite_multiplicado_por_una_constante/</link><dc:creator>José A. Alonso</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;Demostrar con Lean4 que si el límite de la sucesión \(uₙ\) es \(a\) y \(c ∈ ℝ\), entonces el límite de \(cuₙ\) es \(ca\).&lt;/p&gt;
